erver for helping me through the quest.  Now we are off to find a better piercing weapon for Carple!</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Wulfgarin Dergeistdesmonds<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=266075" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=266075</a><br></td></tr>
